01:24.285 --> 01:25.917
[Doorbell rings]

01:25.919 --> 01:27.986
Announcer:<i> And now</i>
<i> back to our programming.</i>

01:27.988 --> 01:30.856
Y-Y-You guys --
You guys stay there.

01:30.858 --> 01:32.591
I'll get it.

01:32.593 --> 01:35.961
<i> [Soft music plays on TV]</i>

01:35.963 --> 01:37.529
Zach's a shapeshifter.

01:37.531 --> 01:40.266
He can p his butt
in the front.

01:40.268 --> 01:43.402
<i> [Zach breathing heavily]</i>
Can he turn his butt
into a wolf?

01:43.404 --> 01:44.870
No.

01:44.872 --> 01:46.605
But his wiener
becomes a tail.

01:46.607 --> 01:51.343
[Inhales sharply]
Oh, Zach, you dirty dog.

01:52.179 --> 01:54.546
Yeah.
Is, uh,
Denise Miller home?

01:54.548 --> 01:56.748
Hold your horses.
[Whistles] Denise!

01:56.750 --> 01:59.718
That won't be necessary.
Here.

02:00.621 --> 02:02.588
Thank you too many.

02:03.490 --> 02:04.623
Uh...

02:04.625 --> 02:06.826
It's, uh, probably
one of those things

02:06.828 --> 02:09.228
