You know what?

02:10.698 --> 02:12.364
I'll tell --
I'll t-tell you what it is.

02:12.366 --> 02:14.099
It's one of those necklaces
that beeps

02:14.101 --> 02:15.634
when you
fall off the toilet.

02:15.636 --> 02:16.902
Not for nothing,

02:16.904 --> 02:18.571
but how in the hell
do you fall off a toilet?

02:18.573 --> 02:21.239
It's shaped like a seat,
for the love of God.

02:21.241 --> 02:23.975
If Elvis had one of those,
he'd still be alive.

02:23.977 --> 02:27.045
Still be alive and big
as a house with a neck...

02:27.047 --> 02:28.914
[Screams, laughs]
Aah!

02:28.916 --> 02:30.482
"Congratulations,
Denise Miller.

02:30.484 --> 02:32.918
You've won the 'Vampire Creek'
Slash Fiction competition

02:32.920 --> 02:34.786
