'Chad The Impaler'!

02:34.788 --> 02:37.322
We want to reward you
with this prop from the show"!

02:37.324 --> 02:39.791
Slash fiction?
Denise, wow.

02:39.793 --> 02:41.660
It's when you write a story
about your favorite show,

02:41.662 --> 02:43.061
like "Star Trek",
but Kirk and Spock are gay

02:43.063 --> 02:45.731
or "Gilmore Girls", but
they're guys and they're gay,

02:45.733 --> 02:48.466
or "Stranger Things",
but it's a movie set in the '90s

02:48.468 --> 02:50.735
and they're --
Yeah, I get -- I get it.

02:50.737 --> 02:52.671
It's my second
favorite hobby.

02:52.673 --> 02:54.273
My first is...

02:54.275 --> 02:55.674
We should open it!

02:55.676 --> 02:56.975
I wonder what it is.

02:57.978 --> 02:59.945
A mirror
from Zach's house!

02:59.947 --> 03:02.681
[Gasping]

03:02.683 --> 03:05.217
♪♪

03:05.219 --> 03:06.751
[Thunder crashes]

03:06.753 --> 03:08.553
[Laughs evilly]

03:08.555 --> 03:17.896
♪♪

03:17.898 --> 03:27.173
♪♪

03:28.242 --> 03:30.509
And you think they're slobs
when they're alive.

03:30.511 --> 03:32.778
Kevin! Kevin!

03:32.780 --> 03:34.245
I won!

03:34.247 --> 03:35.914
My story, "Chad The Impaler",

03:35.916 --> 03:38.116
won the Vampire Creek
Slash Fiction competition.

03:38.118 --> 03:40.119
[Laughs]
What are you doing tonight?

03:40.121 --> 03:42.220
Oh, uh, tonight?

03:42.222 --> 03:44.255
I-I can't tonight.
Let's celebrate tomorrow night!

03:44.257 --> 03:45.991
No, I want to celebrate
tonight.

03:45.993 --> 03:48.059
I'm sorry, Denise.
I have a class.

03:48.061 --> 03:49.594
A what?
[Scoffs]

03:49.596 --> 03:51.797
Do you think all I
want to do with my
life is dig graves?

03:51.799 --> 03:52.931
I mean,
I don't want to brag,

03:52.933 --> 03:55.000
but I always thought
that if I applied myself,

03:55.002 --> 03:58.069
that I could one day,
you know...

03:58.071 --> 03:59.205
What?

03:59.207 --> 04:00.739
Dig swimming pools.

04:00.741 --> 04:03.141
Okay,
you can miss one class.

04:03.143 --> 04:04.443
[Chuckles]

04:04.445 --> 04:06.679
Why don't you tell an astronaut
to miss one class?

04:06.681 --> 04:07.880
Or an assassin.

04:07.882 --> 04:10.249
Or one of those guys
that helps pandas have sex.

04:10.251 --> 04:13.352
They have a very low libido
'cause all they eat is bamboo.

04:13.354 --> 04:14.687
Kevin.

04:14.689 --> 04:15.954
What am I to you?

04:15.956 --> 04:18.990
Am I the real deal,
or am I just some side piece?

04:19.927 --> 04:21.493
What's a side piece?
I don't know,

04:21.495 --> 04:23.028
but they say it a lot
on "Vampire Creek",

04:23.030 --> 04:24.363
and I know it's not good.

04:24.365 --> 04:26.231
But it also makes me
think of chicken,

04:26.233 --> 04:27.098
and now I'm hungry.

04:27.100 --> 04:29.235
[Clears throat]
Later, hater!

04:30.904 --> 04:32.570
[Sighs]

04:32.572 --> 04:34.039
[Water spraying]

04:35.643 --> 04:38.243
Male sex symbol.
Seven letters.

04:38.245 --> 04:39.344
Jack.

04:40.081 --> 04:41.313
Oh.

04:41.315 --> 04:42.847
Klugman.

04:42.849 --> 04:44.350
[Door opens]
Rascal.

04:45.653 --> 04:49.221
Dad,
I am<i> so</i> upset with Kevin.

04:50.090 --> 04:52.157
Prostate flare.

04:52.159 --> 04:53.659
Got to go.

04:55.263 --> 04:57.462
I just wish things
were as romantic

04:57.464 --> 05:00.265
as they are
on "Vampire Creek".

05:00.267 --> 05:01.399
Mirror:
[Whispering] Denise.

05:01.401 --> 05:04.335
Or that cooking show,
"One-Armed Chef."

05:04.337 --> 05:05.804
Denise!

05:05.806 --> 05:08.140
[Sighs] If I was dating
a guy with one arm,

05:08.142 --> 05:10.209
he wouldn't be digging
all the time.

05:10.211 --> 05:11.476
Hello!

05:11.478 --> 05:14.546
Yes, thank you.
Oh. Huh?

05:14.548 --> 05:16.548
Denise.

05:16.550 --> 05:20.819
♪♪

05:20.821 --> 05:23.422
[Portal whirring]

05:23.424 --> 05:24.757
What?!

05:24.759 --> 05:26.825
Whoa.

05:26.827 --> 05:28.160
Zach: Denise!
[Gasps]

05:28.162 --> 05:29.828
♪♪

05:29.830 --> 05:31.163
You're finally here.

05:31.165 --> 05:33.765
Is this Vampire Creek?

05:33.767 --> 05:35.834
Yes, Denise.

05:35.836 --> 05:37.569
I am in love with you.

05:37.571 --> 05:39.437
Oh,
but TV shows aren't real.

05:39.439 --> 05:41.573
Anything is possible
with love.

05:41.575 --> 05:42.775
Is this a dream?
Don't speak.

05:42.777 --> 05:43.709
Okay. I can't.

05:43.711 --> 05:45.710
Everything
you've ever wanted

05:45.712 --> 05:47.245
is in this world.

05:47.247 --> 05:49.315
Cats dressed
as munchkins!
Sure.

05:49.317 --> 05:51.150
Munchkins dressed
as cats!
Yeah, okay, fine.

05:51.152 --> 05:53.118
Giraffes with tap--
Denise, Denise,
Denise, Denise.

05:53.120 --> 05:55.453
There is a reason
I brought you here.

05:55.455 --> 05:57.856
In the world
of the Nosferatu,

05:57.858 --> 05:58.923
there is one night

05:58.925 --> 06:02.060
that towers above
all other nights.

06:02.062 --> 06:04.729
The junior prom of
Vampire Creek High School.

06:04.731 --> 06:06.331
And I want you
to go with me.

06:06.333 --> 06:10.001
[Moans lightly]
I want to go to vampire prom.

06:10.003 --> 06:11.337
But to go,

06:11.339 --> 06:13.672
