one of us.

06:13.674 --> 06:17.342
I am<i> not</i> becoming a boy
to go to prom.

06:17.344 --> 06:18.343
No.

06:18.345 --> 06:19.745
I meant a vampire.

06:19.747 --> 06:21.980
[Gasps]
Just let me bite you,

06:21.982 --> 06:24.549
and you can stay here with me
forever.

06:24.551 --> 06:28.186
If I become a vampire,
can I eat Pop-Tarts?
No.

06:28.188 --> 06:31.289
Can I go home and visit my dad
and all my friends?

06:31.291 --> 06:32.357
No!

06:32.359 --> 06:33.959
But you won't want to,

06:33.961 --> 06:35.360
to watch them age and die

06:35.362 --> 06:37.562
as you live on
through the eons.

06:37.564 --> 06:39.698
And no Pop-Tarts.
No.

06:39.700 --> 06:42.400
I know this is a difficult
decision to make,

06:42.402 --> 06:44.435
but keep in mind,
we have a pretty good chance

06:44.437 --> 06:46.505
of being voted cutest couple
in the yearbook.

06:46.507 --> 06:49.507
Is there any way I could,
like, have a [clears throat]

06:49.509 --> 06:52.845
a trial period?
Figure it out?

06:52.847 --> 06:55.180
I can give you some time
to decide,

06:55.182 --> 06:56.915
but once you commit
to me,

06:56.917 --> 06:59.451
the only way
you can leave this world

06:59.453 --> 07:00.451
is through death!

07:00.453 --> 07:02.287
Oh.
We cool?

07:02.289 --> 07:03.822
Yeah, totes.
All right.

07:03.824 --> 07:06.858
Remember, I am immortal,
but, uh, ticktock.

07:06.860 --> 07:08.693
♪♪

07:12.465 --> 07:14.600
[Insects chirping]

07:14.602 --> 07:16.034
[Clatter in distance]
[Gasps]

07:26.947 --> 07:30.949
♪♪

07:30.951 --> 07:32.751
I knew it.

07:32.753 --> 07:37.489
