we can't win a war.

07:41.495 --> 07:45.029
[Pounding on door]

07:45.031 --> 07:47.299
Aah! Aah.

07:47.301 --> 07:48.566
Stan, it --

07:48.568 --> 07:50.001
i-it's 5:00 in the morning.
