amigos for quite a while.

08:10.991 --> 08:12.591
So, be honest with me.

08:12.593 --> 08:14.726
Did you murder
my daughter?
No!

08:14.728 --> 08:16.461
You buried her alive?
No!

08:16.463 --> 08:17.596
Ya drowned her?
No.

08:17.598 --> 08:19.164
Where'd ya do it?
Winnipesaukee?
No.

08:19.166 --> 08:20.164
Squam?
No.

08:20.166 --> 08:20.932
Kancamagus?
No.

08:20.934 --> 08:22.200
Guilty men would say "no."

08:22.202 --> 08:23.334
Then I<i> did</i> do it!

08:23.336 --> 08:24.202
No!

08:24.204 --> 08:26.805
I don't know
what your game is,

08:26.807 --> 08:30.475
but I'm going to play along
because, Kev,

08:30.477 --> 08:31.743
I'm global.

08:31.745 --> 08:33.945
[Sighs]
[Whistles]

08:33.947 --> 08:36.715
[Whistles]

08:40.888 --> 08:42.888
[Sighs]

08:46.093 --> 08:47.692
[Sniffles]
And no cryin'!

08:47.694 --> 08:49.894
I'm not crying.
You're crying!

08:49.896 --> 08:51.162
[Cries]

08:51.164 --> 08:52.965
