08:52.967 --> 08:56.702
Oh, this house looks
just like it does on TV.

08:56.704 --> 09:00.305
[Gasps]
Oh, it's so cool.

09:00.307 --> 09:01.773
Wow.

09:01.775 --> 09:03.975
[Zach
exhales sharply]

09:03.977 --> 09:05.377
Aah! Hey!

09:05.379 --> 09:06.578
So [chuckles]

09:06.580 --> 09:09.581
you given any more thought
to what we talked about?

09:09.583 --> 09:10.548
