09:10.550 --> 09:12.250
I know this isn't real,

09:12.252 --> 09:13.252
and I-I know
this is a dream.

09:13.254 --> 09:15.987
I-I know everything, okay?
It's just...

09:15.989 --> 09:16.855
I don't know.

09:16.857 --> 09:17.856
