the yearbook.

11:20.247 --> 11:21.579
Please.

11:21.581 --> 11:22.714
[Gulps]

11:22.716 --> 11:24.649
Okay, Denise,
you can do this.

11:24.651 --> 11:33.257
♪♪

11:33.259 --> 11:35.527
Denise!
What are you doing?!

11:35.529 --> 11:38.797
Killing a hobo with a hammer!
What are<i> you</i> doing?!

11:38.799 --> 11:40.799
Stopping you, for one.

11:40.801 --> 11:43.669
It's okay.
This isn't real.

11:43.671 --> 11:46.304
It's a dream,
and now you're in it!

11:46.306 --> 11:47.805
Denise,
this is not a dream.

11:47.807 --> 11:49.607
This is some kind of
tailored reality,

11:49.609 --> 11:51.876
and we got to find a way
to get out of here.

11:51.878 --> 11:54.212
Ah!
Aah!

11:54.214 --> 11:55.012
Aah!

11:55.014 --> 11:56.348
Ah!
Found a can of peaches!

11:56.350 --> 11:58.449
Woman:
I found a can of peaches!

12:01.754 --> 12:04.022
[Cellphone rings, beeps]

12:04.024 --> 12:05.223
Hello?

12:05.225 --> 12:07.159
Leon,
Denise and Evie are missing.

12:07.161 --> 12:08.326
You better get over here.

12:08.328 --> 12:09.561
On my way!

12:09.563 --> 12:11.196
[Cellphone beeps]

12:16.169 --> 12:17.502
[Chuckles]

12:17.504 --> 12:18.769
Buckets.

12:18.771 --> 12:20.906
[Lid opens]

12:20.908 --> 12:22.907
♪♪

12:22.909 --> 12:25.309
[Grunts]

12:25.311 --> 12:27.979
Oh, yeah,
that's the stuff.

12:27.981 --> 12:29.781
[Grunts]

12:29.783 --> 12:31.449
Rise, my child.

12:31.451 --> 12:34.986
♪♪

12:34.988 --> 12:36.454
Aah!
Depeche Mode.

12:36.456 --> 12:37.456
Aah!

12:37.458 --> 12:39.124
Why did you bring
Denise and me here?

12:39.126 --> 12:40.725
You're not even
supposed to be here.

12:40.727 --> 12:42.861
This world was made for Denise.
She was chosen.

12:42.863 --> 12:44.262
Why wasn't<i> I</i> chosen?
[Grunts]

12:44.264 --> 12:45.730
It's not about you.

12:45.732 --> 12:46.965
Then why did you
bite me?!

12:46.967 --> 12:49.968
I wanted to bite Denise,
but it has to be her choice.

12:49.970 --> 12:51.135
Ugh!

12:51.137 --> 12:52.270
Ow!

12:52.272 --> 12:53.671
♪♪

12:53.673 --> 12:55.206
How do I
get outta here?

12:55.208 --> 12:56.341
Oh, that's easy.

12:56.343 --> 12:59.143
Denise just
has to kill you.

12:59.145 --> 13:00.745
Oh!

13:00.747 --> 13:03.014
Peachy.

13:03.016 --> 13:04.749
Ow! Cut my tongue.

13:04.751 --> 13:06.918
So hungry.

13:06.920 --> 13:09.755
Oh, a fridge full of blood.

13:09.757 --> 13:11.289
[Groans]

13:11.291 --> 13:12.824
Zach is back.

13:12.826 --> 13:15.493
Oh, I'm sorry.
Did I scare you, my love?
Yes.

13:15.495 --> 13:19.030
Okay, Zach, we don't always
have to be touching.

13:19.032 --> 13:22.367
What? But how is everybody gonna
know that we're dating, baby?

13:22.369 --> 13:24.435
There's no one here.

13:24.437 --> 13:27.371
Uh, I'm here.
[Scoffs] Not that anyone cares.

13:27.373 --> 13:29.073
♪♪

13:29.075 --> 13:30.208
Zach,
I need aittle space, okay?
Oh.

13:30.210 --> 13:32.243
Do you want to go do that
together?
No!

13:32.245 --> 13:33.711
♪♪

13:33.713 --> 13:35.113
Zach is confused.

13:35.115 --> 13:37.249
[Sighs]

13:37.251 --> 13:39.717
[Shudders]

13:39.719 --> 13:41.653
[Sighs] I miss Kevin.

13:41.655 --> 13:42.754
Oh.

13:42.756 --> 13:44.789
Oh, so you have
two boyfriends now?

13:44.791 --> 13:46.157
[Hisses]
Aah!

13:46.159 --> 13:47.793
Must be nice to be you.

13:49.196 --> 13:50.995
[Sighs deeply]

13:50.997 --> 13:53.731
I'd kill for a ham.

13:53.733 --> 13:54.865
[Sighs]

13:54.867 --> 13:57.202
Like I said, the last time
I saw either one of them

13:57.204 --> 13:59.538
was -- was right here
on this spot

13:59.540 --> 14:01.273
in front of that mirror.

14:01.275 --> 14:02.674
Chew on that for a second,
Leon.

14:02.676 --> 14:04.575
And I'm gonna
go get a beer.

14:05.678 --> 14:08.246
Mirror:
[Whispering] Leon.

14:08.248 --> 14:10.415
[Whispering] What?

14:10.417 --> 14:12.817
What are you reading?

14:12.819 --> 14:15.353
A magazine.

14:15.355 --> 14:16.721
Oh, my gosh.
That's so cool.

14:16.723 --> 14:18.456
Can I see it?

14:18.458 --> 14:20.091
Yes.

14:20.093 --> 14:21.626
Bring it over.

14:21.628 --> 14:25.030
I don't have
my glasses on.

14:25.032 --> 14:27.365
There you go.

14:30.503 --> 14:32.303
Did you know
that mirror can talk?

14:32.305 --> 14:34.105
It keeps
saying my name.

14:34.107 --> 14:35.173
It's a shame Denise left

14:35.175 --> 14:36.975
before she knew
she had a magic mirror.

14:38.345 --> 14:39.510
Oh.

14:39.512 --> 14:41.179
[Up-tempo music plays]

14:41.181 --> 14:43.882
[Indistinct conversations]

14:43.884 --> 14:50.455
♪♪

14:50.457 --> 14:52.056
Okay.

14:52.058 --> 14:53.291
Oh.

14:57.130 --> 15:00.063
Hey, hey, hey. Slow down.
You just turned.

15:00.065 --> 15:03.001
I think I know
what I'm doing, okay?

15:03.003 --> 15:07.672
♪♪

15:07.674 --> 15:08.873
Whew!

15:08.875 --> 15:10.541
Hachi machi.

15:10.543 --> 15:11.742
Ahh.

15:11.744 --> 15:13.744
All right, Leon,
listen carefully.

15:13.746 --> 15:15.213
I'm going in that mirror.

15:15.215 --> 15:17.415
I want you to hang on to --
to that end of the rope,

15:17.417 --> 15:18.716
and don't let go.

15:18.718 --> 15:19.684
You got it?

15:19.686 --> 15:21.853
I won't let you down.
All right.

15:23.090 --> 15:24.622
There you go, pal.

15:24.624 --> 15:27.725
[Portal whirring]

15:27.727 --> 15:29.560
♪♪

15:29.562 --> 15:30.528
No!

15:30.530 --> 15:32.830
Jackass.

15:32.832 --> 15:34.499
Eh.

15:37.303 --> 15:38.670
Stan?!

15:38.672 --> 15:41.640
[Up-tempo music plays]

15:41.642 --> 15:43.675
♪♪

15:43.677 --> 15:45.443
Zach: Evie, slow down.

15:45.445 --> 15:51.182
♪♪

15:51.184 --> 15:52.684
Hey!

15:52.686 --> 15:53.985
You're cute.

15:53.987 --> 15:55.120
What's your name?

15:55.122 --> 15:56.220
Uh-oh.

15:56.222 --> 15:57.255
Bartholomew.

15:57.257 --> 15:58.789
King of the Southern Realm.

15:58.791 --> 16:00.525
Well, Bart...

16:00.527 --> 16:04.262
your name
rhymes with "fart".

16:04.264 --> 16:05.797
Deal with it.

16:05.799 --> 16:07.331
♪♪

16:07.333 --> 16:10.334
[Making fart noises]

16:10.336 --> 16:12.504
[Telephone rings]

16:12.506 --> 16:14.539
Hello?
Stan.

16:14.541 --> 16:15.673
No, this is Leon.

16:15.675 --> 16:17.075
Leon,
what are you doing there?

16:17.077 --> 16:19.277
You're not dating Stan,
are you?

16:19.279 --> 16:22.347
No! I'm talking
to the magic mirror
that ate Denise.

16:22.349 --> 16:23.481
[Chuckling] Oh, good.

16:23.483 --> 16:25.616
Because if you were
dating Stan --

16:25.618 --> 16:27.284
The magic mirror?!

16:27.286 --> 16:29.287
What the hell is this?

16:29.289 --> 16:32.257
Why is everybody
dressed like a pirate?

16:32.259 --> 16:35.226
Evie?
What the hell happened to you?

16:35.228 --> 16:36.260
Stan!

16:36.262 --> 16:38.096
Oh, Stan.

16:38.098 --> 16:40.431
I'm so happy to see you!

16:40.433 --> 16:44.235
You know, earlier tonight,
I met a guy named Fart.

16:44.237 --> 16:46.037
Woman,
have you seen yourself?

16:46.039 --> 16:47.004
Oh, no, I can't.

16:47.006 --> 16:49.173
I don't have a reflection
anymore.

16:49.175 --> 16:51.843
But seriously,
who would name their baby Fart?

16:52.813 --> 16:54.111
Oh!

16:54.113 --> 16:56.047
Yeah!
[Chuckles]

16:56.049 --> 16:57.982
Bye-bye, Stan.

16:57.984 --> 16:59.784
Oh, my God.

17:00.820 --> 17:03.521
Bats are just
hang-gliding mice.

17:03.523 --> 17:05.190
I better tell Fart.

17:05.192 --> 17:07.792
All right, you hang on
to this end of the rope.

17:07.794 --> 17:09.593
I'm going
through the mirror.

17:09.595 --> 17:11.529
You good?
Got it.

17:11.531 --> 17:13.264
Let's do it!

17:13.600 --> 17:14.699
Wait!
You might want to --

17:14.701 --> 17:15.734
[Portal whirring]

17:15.736 --> 17:20.137
♪♪

17:20.139 --> 17:21.406
Oh, shit.

17:21.408 --> 17:22.807
Oh, poop.

17:26.878 --> 17:30.281
[Up-tempo music plays]

17:30.283 --> 17:31.849
Mm.

17:33.420 --> 17:35.286
[Gags]

17:35.288 --> 17:38.756
[Vomits]

17:38.758 --> 17:40.091
Ew!

17:40.093 --> 17:42.694
Ohh.

17:42.696 --> 17:44.863
I'm okay!

17:45.565 --> 17:47.298
Nope.

17:47.300 --> 17:49.367
Don't be mad at me!

17:49.369 --> 17:50.434
[Vomits]

17:50.436 --> 17:51.669
Zach: Everyone?

17:51.671 --> 17:53.905
Excuse me, if I can get
your attention, please.

17:53.907 --> 17:57.642
It is time to announce
prom royalty!

17:57.644 --> 17:58.777
[Applause]

17:58.779 --> 18:00.845
Our beautiful prom queen...

18:00.847 --> 18:02.380
[Vomits]

18:02.382 --> 18:04.048
...D-D-D-Denise!

18:04.050 --> 18:04.983
What?

18:04.985 --> 18:06.451
It's me.

18:06.453 --> 18:08.386
[Laughs]

18:08.388 --> 18:09.987
♪♪

18:09.989 --> 18:11.589
Huh?

18:11.591 --> 18:17.995
♪♪

18:17.997 --> 18:19.464
[Vomits]

18:19.466 --> 18:22.466
♪♪

18:22.468 --> 18:24.702
Time to decide, Denise.

18:24.704 --> 18:26.204
Want to stay here?

18:26.206 --> 18:28.406
-Denise, join us.
-Join us.

18:28.408 --> 18:30.541
The floor is nice.

18:30.543 --> 18:32.143
[Cheers and applause]

18:32.145 --> 18:33.677
Kevin: Denise!

18:33.679 --> 18:35.179
Denise, it's me!

18:35.181 --> 18:37.114
Kevin?

18:37.116 --> 18:38.583
It's me -- Kevin!

18:38.585 --> 18:39.884
[Exhales sharply]

18:39.886 --> 18:42.286
Hi.
I dig graves
in the cemetery!

18:42.288 --> 18:44.689
I-I hear you.
I-I-I see your face.

18:44.691 --> 18:47.625
[Grunting]

18:47.627 --> 18:49.560
Denise!

18:49.562 --> 18:50.862
[Breathing heavily]

18:50.864 --> 18:53.898
Denise, come home.

18:53.900 --> 18:55.299
[Sighs]

18:55.301 --> 18:56.434
I was afraid.

18:56.436 --> 18:57.434
Of what?

18:57.436 --> 18:59.203
[Sighs] I-I was afraid

18:59.205 --> 19:00.838
you'd get to know me

19:00.840 --> 19:02.573
and think I was gross.

19:02.575 --> 19:03.908
No!

19:03.910 --> 19:05.443
Well...
Doesn't matter.

19:05.445 --> 19:07.912
You can't stay here.
This is a fantasy.

19:07.914 --> 19:10.782
This whole thing is something
you want to be real,

19:10.784 --> 19:12.049
and it's not.

19:12.051 --> 19:15.486
Like -- Like guardian angels
or -- or the Hulk.

19:15.488 --> 19:18.456
Ow!
No!

19:18.458 --> 19:20.525
Ohh!

19:20.527 --> 19:22.127
Oh, that hurts!

19:22.129 --> 19:23.061
Yeah.

19:23.063 --> 19:25.462
It's like stepping
on a nail,

19:25.464 --> 19:27.065
but with your neck.

19:27.067 --> 19:29.534
♪♪

19:29.536 --> 19:31.669
All right, Zach,

19:31.671 --> 19:34.338
I will let you
turn me into a vampire.

19:34.340 --> 19:36.107
But please
let my friends go.

19:36.109 --> 19:37.741
The only way
your friends can leave

19:37.743 --> 19:39.476
is if you kill them.

19:39.478 --> 19:43.414
Kill them as in
they'll be...dead?

19:43.416 --> 19:45.550
That's the only way
they can go back.

19:45.552 --> 19:48.285
[Laughs evilly]

19:48.287 --> 19:50.354
[Coughs]

19:50.356 --> 19:52.023
[Groans, clears throat]

19:52.025 --> 19:54.759
[Scoffs] Okay.

19:54.761 --> 19:59.096
Kevin, I really, really
liked what you had to say.

19:59.098 --> 20:00.231
Thanks.

20:01.701 --> 20:02.833
Ohh!

20:02.835 --> 20:04.168
[Crowd gasping]

20:04.170 --> 20:06.904
Ohh!

20:06.906 --> 20:08.606
Denise:
Evie, I'm really sorry,

20:08.608 --> 20:10.374
but I'm gonna have to stab you
through the heart

20:10.376 --> 20:11.776
with this table leg.

20:11.778 --> 20:14.312
Oh, that's okay.
Just don't move me.

20:14.314 --> 20:15.513
Okay.

20:15.515 --> 20:18.382
5, 6, 7, 8.

20:18.651 --> 20:21.652
[Crowd gasps]

20:21.654 --> 20:23.421
You ever found yourself
on the back of a Harley

20:23.423 --> 20:27.858
at sunrise
in Kennebunkport?

20:27.860 --> 20:29.093
No, no.

20:29.095 --> 20:30.428
Now,
don't you go turning me

20:30.430 --> 20:32.596
into a sparkling pile
of lady dust.

20:32.598 --> 20:36.934
Dad, I think I'm gonna enjoy
killing you most of all.

20:36.936 --> 20:38.269
No, no.

20:38.771 --> 20:41.271
No! Ohh!

20:41.273 --> 20:43.541
Aah!

20:44.211 --> 20:47.145
[Crowd gasps]

20:47.147 --> 20:49.380
[Breathing heavily]

20:49.382 --> 20:51.081
It's time, Denise.

20:51.083 --> 20:53.217
This world
was made for you.

20:53.219 --> 20:56.153
I know.
That's the problem.

20:56.756 --> 21:00.224
Aah!
Ohh, you can't kill Zach!

21:00.226 --> 21:03.160
Obviously, you can.
I'm just being dramatic.

21:03.162 --> 21:04.962
♪♪

21:04.964 --> 21:07.365
[Crowd gasps, murmuring]

21:07.367 --> 21:09.100
Still the queen, though,
right?

21:09.102 --> 21:12.169
[Crowd murmuring]

21:12.171 --> 21:13.438
Yeah!

21:15.375 --> 21:16.640
Is everyone okay?

21:16.642 --> 21:18.909
This never happened.

21:18.911 --> 21:21.713
Is everybody
understood on that?

21:21.715 --> 21:24.582
Uh-huh.

21:24.584 --> 21:26.384
So, my plan worked.

21:26.386 --> 21:30.321
♪♪

21:30.323 --> 21:32.089
Mirror:
[Whispering] Bye, nerds.
